This SCP was an interesting one Here’s the thing, I like the overall idea of the SCP and the story behind it for the most part was interesting aside from a few small errors I found that most people won’t even notice as I like to critique. I think the characters need a bit of work though, we don’t exactly know who many of the characters are such as Bond and the Poi and though you tried to include some background details I found that still quite lacking and the storyline sort of expects us to already know what happened before even though we obviously don’t. I could list a few other things including character development as we see Bond does not change his mind or make a deal as far as we know with the Poi so the whole story does end up resulting in not much of a comforting and conclusive ending. Honestly though I could not write a better story and I think later comments will help you better from more experienced site members as I only just started making reviews of SCPs instead of reading this for the last three years and I’m going to remain neutral for now and see what happens to this SCP in a few months and rate it then.







